    <p>Sip on be­spoke LoveSG cock­tails ($11.90++ each) that draw in­spi­ra­tion from Sin­ga­pore’s rich her­itage. They in­clude KopiKwah (or­ganic cachaca rum, black kopi, con­densed milk, caramel syrup and chin chow), Ban­dung Sen­sa­tion (Tan­glin gin, vi­o­lettes, co­conut cream and straw­berry syrup) and Gim­let of the East (lemon­grass-in­fused gin, fresh lime juice and honey wa­ter). WHERE: Cross­roads, Sin­ga­pore Mar­riott Tang Plaza Ho­tel,</p>
    <p>320 Or­chard Road MRT: Or­chard WHEN: 11am - 10.30pm</p>
    <p>TEL: 6735-5800</p>
    <p>INFO: bit.ly/2H2Umwe</p>


